{"type": "article", "id": 19558, "title": "浮雕花纹瓷砖", "description": "", "date": "2015-12-23T07:37:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606144325dtJnXTCho4O9Yj8z.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t英国设计师 Lindsey Lang 根据伦敦在 1930 年代的地铁系统设计了这一系列瓷砖，瓷砖表面有两种浮雕的花纹。一种是菱形网格的，源于伊妮德·马克思(Enid Marx）在 1938 年左右的绘画。另一种是圆圈型的，是从艺术家 Harold Stabler 处获得的灵感。这一系列瓷砖有多种颜色，组合在一起时有清新自然的艺术效果。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150035IJdvh0iAPm3TWy5w.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150036khurAiQRVovXE1pq.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"771\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150036FQj8hnXEAt3lVbUa.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150037nsAGk3TKW7xEiQmU.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"936\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726150037VQ6kR5w9Dyhxt4AC.jpg\" width=\"936\" height=\"1313\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.40277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}